WEBVTT

00:02.370 --> 00:05.521
- Previously:
- Hannibal!
- We are as close as we are

00:05.570 --> 00:08.459
ever going to get
to catching this man.

00:08.500 --> 00:11.708
- I'm dismantling who I was
and moving it brick by brick.

00:11.740 --> 00:15.528
It's the last stage
of a transformation.
We could disappear now.

00:15.580 --> 00:18.799
- You've set some
sort of trap and you're
goading Hannibal into it.

00:18.850 --> 00:22.342
- How can you be sure he's
not goading you?
- I can't.

00:22.390 --> 00:25.518
- I have begun to
question your actions

00:25.550 --> 00:29.429
