03:05.780 --> 03:09.216
- Antony Dimmond.
- Boris Jakov.

03:09.250 --> 03:11.741
- I'd offer a hand, but...
- It's a double-fisted

03:11.790 --> 03:14.486
kind of bash.

03:14.520 --> 03:17.318
- Do you know
Roman well?

03:17.360 --> 03:18.952
You were staring with
the thinly-veiled disdain

03:18.990 --> 03:22.869
