07:40.090 --> 07:43.480
You smoked me in thyme.

07:43.530 --> 07:48.058
- Smoked, glazed, served
on a sugar cane quill.

07:48.100 --> 07:51.228
You will be
falling off the bone.

07:51.270 --> 07:54.967
- Well, of course. And
with these rarified dishes

07:55.000 --> 07:56.968
