18:07.220 --> 18:10.542
- Well, you're in no position
to ask, Dr. Du Maurier.

18:10.590 --> 18:14.310
You ended our patient-
psychiatrist relationship.

18:17.260 --> 18:21.799
- I lacked the appropriate
skills to continue your therapy.

18:24.200 --> 18:27.590
- I never found you
to be lacking.

18:30.210 --> 18:32.531
- I'm sorry I didn't provide you

18:32.570 --> 18:34.879
with a suitable
substitute for therapy.

18:37.650 --> 18:41.677
Is Will Graham still alive?

18:44.650 --> 18:48.586
- Will Graham was not a suitable
substitute for therapy.

18:51.260 --> 18:53.421
- What was he?

18:53.460 --> 18:56.793
_- Is this _ _
profeSSIonal curIOSIty?

18:56.830 --> 18:59.799
- Almost entirely.

19:05.510 --> 19:07.307
- Do you trust me?

19:10.350 --> 19:12.306
- Not entirely.

19:12.350 --> 19:14.910
- Are you taking
into consideration

19:14.950 --> 19:17.316
my beliefs about
your intentions?

19:17.350 --> 19:20.387
- My intentions?

19:20.420 --> 19:25.323
-_ Human motivation can be
lIttle more than IUCld greed.

19:25.360 --> 19:27.396
- Greed...

